data.description: Awesome open floor plan on an oversized lot.  3 level split home has a main living area that is great for gathering, large lower level family room with wood burning fireplace, and large windows. 3 big bedrooms, 1 full and one 1/2 bathroom. The backyard is huge and fully fenced with large deck and storage shed. Move in ready! Convenient location!
